This query will return the employee number, name, and date of birth for those who will reach the age of sixty in 2026. The condition `YEAR(TODAY) - YEAR(date_of_birth) + 1 = 60` checks if the employee will turn sixty in 2026. The additional conditions `MONTH(TODAY) > MONTH(date_of_birth)` and `(MONTH(TODAY) = MONTH(date_of_birth) AND DAY(TODAY) >= DAY(date_of_birth))` ensure that the employee has not already turned sixty.
